        "lang.en": "EN",
        "hero.title": "At <span class='highlight'>AulaSPUTNIK</span> we embark on a new education in values",
        "hero.button1": "Our Workshops &nbsp;<i class='fa-solid fa-arrow-right'></i>",
        "hero.button2": "The AulaSPUTNIK Challenge &nbsp;<i class='fa-solid fa-arrow-right'></i>",
        "hero.scrollDown": "Learn More",
        "context.title": "CONTEXT",
        "context.para1": "In the context of the new society we are building, an uncertain and complex one, it is very important to <strong>develop and open new capacities</strong> for people to learn to cooperate and participate. Therefore, it is crucial for a collective to empower itself and build from scientific method, critical thinking, and <strong>inspiration</strong>.",
        "context.para2": "The scientific and technological world is a remote field for many people. For this reason, humanizing science and technology is a fundamental challenge, especially when we talk about the aerospace sector. The aerospace sector is a field that <strong>drives</strong> the improvement of academic and employability skills, and also innovates to <strong>find solutions</strong> to new social challenges like climate change.",
        "context.para3": "For this reason, education and the aerospace sector are two key factors for advancing these collective future challenges. New generations are the <strong>key</strong> to building a more cooperative, leading, and inclusive society, where any person <strong>regardless of gender, context, age, or culture</strong>, can have equal opportunities.",
        "accordion.objective": "OBJECTIVE",
        "accordion.objectiveContent": "AulaSPUTNIK is an educational project aimed at conducting activities to inspire and awaken the talent of new generations, with the aerospace sector as context, in an inclusive, accessible, and participatory way for all contexts. We believe in the development of scientific-technological competence, understood as a basic competence (and therefore indispensable) for all people and based on values.",
        "accordion.mission": "MISSION",
        "accordion.missionContent": "The mission is to develop positive attitudes, emotions, and identities related to science and society; therefore, the target audience focuses on people from 8 to 88 years old. We will learn the importance of social participation and leadership in science and improve academic and employability skills, with the aerospace sector as context.",
        "accordion.vision": "VISION",
        "accordion.visionContent": "Our vision is to awaken curiosity and creativity, as well as personal capacities and teamwork. We want to motivate and educate, and thus expand opportunities to relate with science.",
