        "workshop.5.summary": "An imaginative journey into the search for extraterrestrial life. Students explore the biological requirements for life and imagine what life might look like on other worlds.",
        "workshop.5.summary2": "Combines biology, chemistry, and imagination to design alien organisms adapted to planets with extreme conditions.",
        "workshop.5.learning1": "The basic requirements for life and panspermia.",
