        "equip.pageTitle": "Our Team",
        "equip.lead1": "Projects are built thanks to the people who dedicate their time and energy to making small tasks a reality. For us, the value of teamwork is crucial. That is why AulaSPUTNIK is the energy, motivation and heart of the human team we are.",
        "equip.lead2": "<strong>Want to get to know us?</strong>",
        "team.anna.title": "Coordinator and Social Media",
        "team.anna.bio": "Graduated in Aerospace Systems Engineering and Science Communication, she has united her two passions: space and people. Her curiosity and desire to transform the world led her to create this educational project where emotions, values, and science come together in every workshop.",
        "team.anna.quote": "“I want children to look at the sky, not only to dream, but also to understand the world they inhabit”",
        "team.ana.title": "Science Communicator and Workshop Creator",
        "team.ana.bio": "Graduated in Architecture and specialised in Space Architecture, she manages to combine her passion for space and astronomy with education.",
        "team.ana.quote": "“Let us make new generations feel capable of exploring and boosting their innate curiosity to turn what has until now been science fiction into reality”",
        "team.jaume.title": "Science Communicator and Workshop Creator",
        "team.jaume.bio": "With a background focused on Space Biotechnology and Synthetic Biology, he develops innovative solutions through strategic research to improve life on Earth and open paths toward the future of space exploration.",
        "team.jaume.quote": "“Space exploration begins within us. Only when we ignite curiosity, creativity and the desire to explore, can we truly go further.”",
        "team.linkedinBtn": "Connect with me",
        "projectes.pageTitle": "Our Projects",
        "projectes.lead": "At AulaSPUTNIK we believe in collaborating with other entities, foundations, and projects to have a greater impact on society. We also believe in the exchange of learnings and experiences, which helps us grow as a project and as people. In this section, we share some of our initiatives.",
        "projectes.challengeTitle": "The AulaSPUTNIK Challenge",
        "projectes.challengeSubtitle": "A unique space mission that combines all our workshops into an unforgettable experience.",
        "projectes.challengeBtn": "Learn more",
        "projectes.fcriTitle": "FCRI Grant 2022",
        "projectes.fcriBio1": "The AulaSPUTNIK project received an economic grant in 2022 from the Catalan Foundation for Research and Innovation (FCRI). With this grant, AulaSPUTNIK was able to run 20 workshops at different schools and centres in the Bages, Anoia and Osona counties.",
        "projectes.fcriBio2": "More than 400 boys and girls from Catalonia had the opportunity to experience an AulaSPUTNIK workshop. They learnt about how nanosatellites help society, worked as a team building a rocket, and reflected on the biases we hold towards certain professions by meeting women in the aerospace sector.",
        "projectes.collaboratorsTitle": "Collaborators",
