        "legal.modificationsTitle": "MODIFICATIONS",
        "legal.modificationsContent": "Ruiz Ayala, Anna reserves the right to make any changes it deems appropriate to its portal without prior notice, and may change, remove or add both the content and services provided through it, as well as the way in which they appear or are located.",
        "legal.linksTitle": "LINKS",
